headline: Stanley Black & Decker Announces Release Date for Second Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) will broadcast its second quarter 2025 earnings webcast on Tuesday, July 29, 2025. The webcast will begin at 8:00AM ET.
